    <div class="prose">
      <h2 id="program-heading">What a program looks like</h2>
      <p>Every program pairs a working edible garden with hands-on soil education: what lives in healthy soil, why compost works, and how food actually gets its nutrients. Sessions are practical and curriculum-adjacent — students test, plant, feed and harvest.</p>
      <p>Programs are shaped with the school: raised-bed builds, soil and compost setup, classroom sessions, and a maintenance plan teachers and parent volunteers can actually keep up.</p>
      <p>Dedicated kids' programming is growing into its own brand alongside Coastal Soil Solutions — ask us about it on a program call.</p>
    </div>
